ObjectStack uses folder-scoped dual licensing.

Different folders in this monorepo are released under different licenses. See
LICENSING.md for the folder-level license map. Published package manifests
mirror these rules through their package.json "license" fields.

Summary
-------

- Everything is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 by default. The
  full text is in LICENSE.apache.

- Only packages/services/* and packages/plugins/* are licensed under the
  Business Source License 1.1, with a Change Date four years after each release
  at which the license converts to Apache License, Version 2.0. The full text is
  in LICENSE.bsl.

For details, see LICENSING.md in this directory.

For commercial licensing inquiries, contact licensing@objectstack.dev.
